channel.title: Can't log into any server
channel.description: Everytime I try to use any server straight from the up and running list, it tells me that there has been an error connecting to the server and that it must be down. If i try to do the create your own server thing, i get the same message. What do I do? :confused:

item.title: Can't log into any server
item.dc:creator: @system system
item.description:
@system wrote:

Maybe you have an internet firewall that’s stopping you connection to servers and thats blocking mopar’s (or whatever client you use) access to the internet.
